                                "content": "Reed-Sternberg cells are present."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "acc070dd76594808af4fe8b37a578d25",
                                "content": "The lymph nodes, spleen, and liver are involved."
